| Set a system variable to point to the current directory
Set PsiFS$Dir <Obey$Dir>

| Load the application sprites
If "<Boot$OSVersion>" < "400" Then IconSprites <PsiFS$Dir>.!Sprites Else IconSprites <PsiFS$Dir>.4Sprites